channel.title: 508 Server Trouble
channel.description:
Hello There.
I am having trouble when i try to load up a 508 server I recently tried to make a server, but it just would work so i stopped. But it seems that when i try to load up a 508 server, or even a 317 server; it wont let me load up. Im not sure what i did wrong, but i have a laptop and the servers work perfectly fine of them. I think its something i did wrong on the settings when i tried to make a server. So can anyone give me tips; or just help me through this?
Thanks;
BloodyBooger.

[quote=“tracuer93, post:2, topic:293551”]well u need a 508 client+cache to to be able to log into ur 508 server

Yeah, I already have it downloaded. But when i run it; it just opens and closes up in a split second.
Ugh, this is harder than expected.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: August 17, 2009, 03:53:20 am[/size][hr]Any more suggestions? And when i try the IP changer, the same thing happeneds, it opens up, and closes up really fast.

PLEASE HELP!!
